  "metadata": {
    "individual_metadata": {
      "PAD": {
        "synopsis": "The player witnesses a bloody corpse rolling out of the chute in the Cleansing Room of the lower Mind Flayer Colony, coming in from the Oubliette. This PAD is their reaction to seeing this, and connecting it to Moonrise above.",
        "how_to_trigger": "In the lower floor of the Mind Flayer Colony, find your way to the Cleansing Room. In here, there is a large chute leading in from the (inaccessible) Oubliette on the other side. Approach the chute and press the illithid console button next to it, and a corpse will come rolling out. A short moment afterwards, this PAD will play as a reaction to this. The corpse will only roll out once, and this PAD will also only play once."
      },
      "Corpse_Dead": {
        "synopsis": "The Speak With Dead dialog for the default fallback corpse that drops from the Cleansing Chute corpse. This corpse only appears when another minor character (presumably one of the tieflings) shouldn't end up dead here for some reason.",
        "how_to_trigger": "Go to the lower floor of the Colony, to the Cleansing Room chute. Press the button on the console to drop the body out of the chute (happens only once). This corpse appearing requires no flags at the moment, but will require some in the future. Give yourself a Speak With Dead spell through ReCon and cast it onto the corpse."
      },
      "PAD_BloodShower": {
        "synopsis": "A player reacts to getting splattered in blood and guts when they are standing below the corpse chute of the Colony Cleansing Room, when it is opened up. On the first time, a corpse will come falling out, but afterwards the chute simply serves as a blood shower at the press of the button.",
        "how_to_trigger": "In the lower floor of the Mind Flayer Colony, find your way to the Cleansing Room. In here, there is a large chute leading in from the (inaccessible) Oubliette on the other side. Place one player character beneath the corpse chute/tentacle, and let another press the button to open the chute. Blood will spurt out and the player getting sprayed will react to this."
      }
    },
    "source_files": [
      "COL_CleansingChute_PAD.json",
      "COL_CleansingChute_Corpse_Dead.json",
      "COL_CleansingChute_PAD_BloodShower.json"
    ]
  },
